H0.text: Pandalus borealis is more commonly called (and officially named by the UN Food and Agriculture Organization). Northern Shrimp

H1.text: Pandalus borealis is more commonly called (and officially named by the UN Food and Agriculture Organization). Coldwater Prawn

H2.text: Pandalus borealis is more commonly called (and officially named by the UN Food and Agriculture Organization). Boreal Shrimp

H3.text: Pandalus borealis is more commonly called (and officially named by the UN Food and Agriculture Organization). Ama-ebi

A4.text: The Food and Agriculture Organization refers to them as the northern prawn.

A5.text: Other common names include pink shrimp, deepwater prawn, deep-sea prawn, Nordic shrimp, great northern prawn, northern shrimp, coldwater prawn and Maine shrimp.
